  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Secretary of State for Wales Simon Hart takes part in event to highlight changes to the immigration and visa system after the end of the EU Transition Period. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
